task.summary: Default task
Updated typescript task so that typescript files and javascript files are separated in different directories.
Migration of project to latest angular 2 version(2.0.0-rc1) with sanity check.
Fixed collapsable popouts,removed search bar and tags,added icons for files and folders along with checkbox,and added material design icons.
Completed prototype interface including UI of the popouts,delete confirmation modal,file dialog on browse of move, and folder name as being typed in the group popout.
Completed basic file operations:move,copy,rename,delete and group. A few new dependencies added: fs-extra,trash and mv.Refresh of file explorer and error handling pending.
Added progress bar with functional backend,notification at the end of each file operation,and deletion/move now removes files from the UI.
Added a dummy generator command line utility(as a gulp task) that generates random file structure on disk for testing purposes.
Introduced scan targets and updated data items with dummy data generation(untested) utility, also introduced menu and feedback components.
Scan targets list shows up in the menu sidebar,opening and closing of main menu
Refactored context component to introduce certain new components for sunburst chart, and its usage details along with a toggle view button.
Integrated designs in the organize section particularly the popouts, delete box and the subheader. No animation yet though.
Migrated to RC3 of angular2, integrated designs in the main menu (except feedback)
Implemented designs in the feedback section with animation and the sort by menu.
Integrated designs for the analyze screen and implemented all the animations on toggling between analyze and organize screen.
Implemented selection feature using dragging gesture and other key combinations in both screens.Design phase integration completed.
Implemented scanning algorithm,sorting feature and refactored the design to eliminate context object and use data item tree instead.
Implemented sunburst chart, redesign the main menu,fixed the callbacks of the operations and fixed progress bar to show at the bottom.
Fixed a few ui issues(breadcrumb,data area),implemeted improved scanning algorithm, organized data service callback classes.
Completed scanning of folder targets with progress bar,clicking on a scan target opens its sunburst(works with multiple targets also)
Sunburst replaced with circle pack for just one layer
Reverted back to sunburst and added classes for secondary display tree for the sunburst
Improved performance of the sunburst by using a compressed secondary display tree
Further reduced count of elements in the sunburst chart
Implemented folder navigation during sunburst transitions
Zoomable navigation works with more details added to the display tree in the click handler
Implemented zoom animation on the display tree albeit with a few NaN bugs
Cleaned up sunburst code that utilizes optimized display tree and fixed a few bugs
Moved display tree ownership to scan target and implemented move back animation in sunburst chart
Usage detail now uses display tree and displays a "more" button for omitted items.
"more" button functionality implemented and usage detail is now scrollable.
Formatted the design of the usage details to be more "spaced out"
Fixed multiple selection using shift in usage detail and incorrect size bug in sunburst
Implemented sort to toggle between ascending and descending when sort option is chosen repeatedly.
Implemented rolling animation when hovered over data item name in usage detail
Fixed selection box bug which selects nearby elements even when they are not overlapping
Fixed buggy selection box preventing selection of items after scrolling down
Fixed scanning algorithm that failed earlier on symlinks
Moved Display element tree population to scan target and cleaned up a few typescript errors
Made sunburst chart in sync with navigation in the organise section while opening folders
Navigation through the breadcrumb now affects the sunburst chart
Minor redesign of the main menu and certain action buttons
Implemented rainbow coloring in the sunburst chart
Fixed upward drag in the selection box after the user has scrolled down.
